{"tid":25283,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養龍貓，新手求教學","createTime":"2016-12-06T04:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T15:44:23.000Z","uid":19727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0876c08baf4702cc2550391b2a726f854bda8e6","tid":25283,"uid":19727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"一直自己都想養龍貓好耐<br />\n但見香港好似好少人養<br />\n而且又唔知點養<br />\n希望有養既爸絲可以講下有咩洗費<br />\n同埋要點樣養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5622ef9b33b7837ffa624a8648ffbb0ce5f55361","tid":25283,"uid":57530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"龍巴士"},{"pid":"3b89a2f4c53545b0eb3ef188e3759f1bcde0a954","tid":25283,"uid":3524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"我有養兔<br />\n好耐之前龍貓都有睇過下，都好容易養，唔需要沖涼，糞便無味，主要食草。比起兔，免疫力高好多"},{"pid":"43edd9fae9bf139d1f2e16a218baf9eb3879908f","tid":25283,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"上網睇過,一隻顏色普通的龍貓大約$1500,另類的顏色大約$4000"},{"pid":"cb2fe19cff9e1ae958fbef0ee7c7fd8317f3827c","tid":25283,"uid":60670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"痴唔痴人㗎？如果同時想養狗又得唔得呢？"},{"pid":"ba2587eaa7c9b48906c0c9e9d430f0b862164a4f","tid":25283,"uid":44147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"有朋友養緊三隻，一對係孖黎，勁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62761b4e0737070109e45cf31add1d7e3ad5178","tid":25283,"uid":28035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴唔痴人㗎？如果同時想養狗又得唔得呢？</blockquote><br />\n好似睇隻野性格<br />\n如果隻鼠唔惡，鐘意同其他野玩<br />\n狗又無脾氣，主人睇住應該得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個籠都會放高"},{"pid":"8fc469277c89cf36fe2f659ea4e008c4083321b1","tid":25283,"uid":30005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:14:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母696</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2244435b6e591a94f8ca6c611e40b1f4c31680bf","tid":25283,"uid":30005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母696</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂回錯post"},{"pid":"6602538ed3dc3b728dd22b3e186f6c4f729fa299","tid":25283,"uid":2732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母696</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂回錯post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b122695967c8600dec056c494a4ac8d5eb743c1a","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"日常洗費都係草，糧，尿墊同沖涼沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實龍貓好易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又少病痛又長命<br />\n最重要係佢地超得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個波咁"},{"pid":"7ac0e53a1e2daed1b02f056901d0e3eb115c862e","tid":25283,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"老鼠來。好嘈"},{"pid":"e1a3e650bf8334b333e6744ab5b627854d0291d9","tid":25283,"uid":61464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"養咗6年，一隻，仔嚟的<br />\n平時日頭訓覺，夜晚起身<br />\n絕大多數情況都好安靜<br />\n每日清潔(換木糠)就唔有異味<br />\n主糧係草，配合少量龍貓糧<br />\n鍾意食寵物零食，有時會餵佢食生果<br />\n鍾意同人玩，我嗰隻極鍾意俾人摸<br />\n算係幾聰明，識用手攞嘢食<br />\n唔咬人，定期幫佢沖涼(用沖涼粉)<br />\n夏天最好有把風扇仔吹吓佢，因為佢啲毛好厚，所以其實都好好摸<br />\n日頭屋企最好唔好咁嘈。"},{"pid":"51cc6400327732e1af2f75e68aca2b490d3d65b1","tid":25283,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"好得意好想養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0805ab0af506061d7ba79498f0faba7bd451335","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老鼠來。好嘈</blockquote><br />\n佢地除左唔開心同嬲果陣先會叫咋wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都算嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0ab276b1b6568c034c22fad1c0350f6093ef39","tid":25283,"uid":18707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:35:39.000Z","msg":"唔好放入房養  夜晚跳上跳落嘈到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cf35a6827cad69e176dd5bc297f10f33ee6f3f","tid":25283,"uid":29140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"龍貓好撚多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8820ba7df323927765209d949f5d7225596768","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍貓好撚多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好睬唔臭"},{"pid":"857b18624c10306585b040e15bf8d33c1a6d8308","tid":25283,"uid":19727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍貓好撚多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好難清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9492ebd2ad188760d1b980e07f9dece9d2d7fb0","tid":25283,"uid":19727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好放入房養  夜晚跳上跳落嘈到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗同倉鼠差唔多？"},{"pid":"f07cdb2dccdca218d95f98aca0183392299d3121","tid":25283,"uid":19727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養咗6年，一隻，仔嚟的<br />\n平時日頭訓覺，夜晚起身<br />\n絕大多數情況都好安靜<br />\n每日清潔(換木糠)就唔有異味<br />\n主糧係草，配合少量龍貓糧<br />\n鍾意食寵物零食，有時會餵佢食生果<br />\n鍾意同人玩，我嗰隻極鍾意俾人摸<br />\n算係幾聰明，識用手攞嘢食<br />\n唔咬人，定期幫佢沖涼(用沖涼粉)<br />\n夏天最好有把風扇仔吹吓佢，因為佢啲毛好厚，所以其實都好好摸<br />\n日頭屋企最好唔好咁嘈。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見人講話要買抽濕機"},{"pid":"43c9b6adf1ebec2f599bb5afe3af14f1066b582e","tid":25283,"uid":61464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>養咗6年，一隻，仔嚟的<br />\n平時日頭訓覺，夜晚起身<br />\n絕大多數情況都好安靜<br />\n每日清潔(換木糠)就唔有異味<br />\n主糧係草，配合少量龍貓糧<br />\n鍾意食寵物零食，有時會餵佢食生果<br />\n鍾意同人玩，我嗰隻極鍾意俾人摸<br />\n算係幾聰明，識用手攞嘢食<br />\n唔咬人，定期幫佢沖涼(用沖涼粉)<br />\n夏天最好有把風扇仔吹吓佢，因為佢啲毛好厚，所以其實都好好摸<br />\n日頭屋企最好唔好咁嘈。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見人講話要買抽濕機</blockquote><br />\nnot a must"},{"pid":"1f6c430cd4539c08ecd0795857f04e6e8c955ce4","tid":25283,"uid":28035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前買d手指餅肯食，依家買一樣既又唔撚食<br />\n仆街老鼠懶得意，一時一樣煩過港女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bca51b88de19b47ba6aa8f573de188ddace494","tid":25283,"uid":28035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前買d手指餅肯食，依家買一樣既又唔撚食<br />\n仆街老鼠懶得意，一時一樣煩過港女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚想卒爆佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaed7caf7e70edf2de9f77bdb30400525a315ad","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>龍貓好撚多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好難清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除非佢有病屙爛屎"},{"pid":"a7d9e26f7da5018d35b20f1f2871e206a80ac557","tid":25283,"uid":61464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"劉明"},{"pid":"a752fe796d9d510d4d97ed88c83e231e72219b99","tid":25283,"uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:01:14.000Z","msg":"夜晚出沒，咬野好嘈，會換毛，鼻敏感就盡量唔好養<br />\n高寵、草、糧、跳板、磨牙既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然鼻敏感左19年，不過我好愛佢😘 ，我隻龍貓差唔多5歲喇，有咩即管問"},{"pid":"8a78d419e077d7982b614bbd55ffb99e2316c7d3","tid":25283,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"點解出邊賣 越大越貴？<br />\n同其他寵物相反（烏龜例外） 唔係由細細個養起好d咩"},{"pid":"2036d7775ee5a0b5e11170b3ec5b1a4d67f6896a","tid":25283,"uid":61989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:50:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0688e3ca500b6c7e6d46f158235c3381c6219b36","tid":25283,"uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解出邊賣 越大越貴？<br />\n同其他寵物相反（烏龜例外） 唔係由細細個養起好d咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔關年齡事，係關佢隻色同純唔純種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb350a3b56373a251e204096ed946e67cad11dbe","tid":25283,"uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"草既話買first cut，對佢地磨牙會好啲！<br />\n<br />\n我唔會買磨牙石，因為無咁天然，我會俾仙人掌木佢咬"},{"pid":"eaf4bde1a5efe00c656dfbb94f8a20d0f73e00f2","tid":25283,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解出邊賣 越大越貴？<br />\n同其他寵物相反（烏龜例外） 唔係由細細個養起好d咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔關年齡事，係關佢隻色同純唔純種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見就咁寫龍貓 冇專登分門別類 <br />\n得歲數同價錢<br />\n越大真係越貴 4歲去到差唔多10000<br />\n得十幾年命"},{"pid":"f09b5001f194dec17a610910d93081f734438b1b","tid":25283,"uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解出邊賣 越大越貴？<br />\n同其他寵物相反（烏龜例外） 唔係由細細個養起好d咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔關年齡事，係關佢隻色同純唔純種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見就咁寫龍貓 冇專登分門別類 <br />\n得歲數同價錢<br />\n越大真係越貴 4歲去到差唔多10000<br />\n得十幾年命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個真係唔清楚<br />\n不過我估<br />\n純種純色，跟貴同平去排<br />\ne.g 白色》銀灰》灰色<br />\n<br />\n但貴既可以貴到萬幾蚊既純種白色龍貓，<br />\n所以賣唔出都唔奇！<br />\n可能先有錯覺年紀愈大愈貴。<br />\n<br />\n其實賣龍貓既地方唔止一兩間，<br />\n要養既上網search多幾間先買！<br />\n<br />\nBetween，我係養灰色，人地送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗錢<br />\n不過幾隻色入面，我覺得灰色最可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25974d294ff64f18f16114eccfbd7cf1518307c","tid":25283,"uid":49825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"一定要養!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d302c6630b65161ccf471a0c5031d22a16037","tid":25283,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"Xboxone Contana留名系統過熱，請勿站在系統附近。"},{"pid":"684f3802845d8bbe6e46436b22d06db82178d593","tid":25283,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"男朋友有隻<br />\n可愛到不得了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔咬人<br />\n又唔大味<br />\n同佢玩佢好嗲人<br />\n同埋摸落去真係好舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來我都麻麻地龍貓<br />\n見多幾次都中意左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過都係睇隻野性格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87961d0482ae817d98eea83258d2d54048597a4e","tid":25283,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養龍貓之前諗清楚  佢地有機會有15-20年壽命  要養就唔該養佢一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千奇唔好放生<br />\n<br />\n另外如果想玩龍貓育成計劃  生完隻b出黎 <br />\n爸爸 同 媽媽 同bb 要分返性別去養 （bb食完三四個月 母乳先） 因為絕育手術對龍貓都危險 <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地要食好多草  食唔夠就會有內牙長既問題  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qzk52Hu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzk52Hu.jpg&h=8210c727&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛"},{"pid":"b45913eb943b9255cebe2a88ed4c8b9153951787","tid":25283,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>養龍貓之前諗清楚  佢地有機會有15-20年壽命  要養就唔該養佢一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千奇唔好放生<br />\n<br />\n另外如果想玩龍貓育成計劃  生完隻b出黎 <br />\n爸爸 同 媽媽 同bb 要分返性別去養 （bb食完三四個月 母乳先） 因為絕育手術對龍貓都危險 <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地要食好多草  食唔夠就會有內牙長既問題  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qzk52Hu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzk52Hu.jpg&h=8210c727&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知幾隻一齊養會唔會打交？"},{"pid":"115f7f652df009137a438b62cefbacbc43f672c9","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養龍貓之前諗清楚  佢地有機會有15-20年壽命  要養就唔該養佢一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千奇唔好放生<br />\n<br />\n另外如果想玩龍貓育成計劃  生完隻b出黎 <br />\n爸爸 同 媽媽 同bb 要分返性別去養 （bb食完三四個月 母乳先） 因為絕育手術對龍貓都危險 <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地要食好多草  食唔夠就會有內牙長既問題  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qzk52Hu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzk52Hu.jpg&h=8210c727&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知幾隻一齊養會唔會打交？</blockquote><br />\n多數唔會，佢地群居動物黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個籠一定要夠大"},{"pid":"8e698aa58d48599e1d1a6fc693b9e9444521a370","tid":25283,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2ad4a1ce3509603ee865873041808641cf5f011","tid":25283,"uid":34668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:23:17.000Z","msg":"我之前有養2隻龍貓<br />\n<br />\nd屎細細粒 成粒米咁好搞笑<br />\n<br />\n不過超細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb43443f9749f4705552666f4c5836862e638063","tid":25283,"uid":14016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:27:42.000Z","msg":"夜晚好嘈 個籠好大 成日係度跳黎跳去<br />\n果時隻龍貓成日蝦我隻狗 成日引我隻狗行過 之後咬佢個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛好聰明"},{"pid":"286ff23aa845a9e8cfab601c8bf9e24bc1d34374","tid":25283,"uid":18370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg&h=e258ceb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人會買跑碟/跑輪（35cm) 比佢地玩<br />\n有無咩玩具岩佢地玩"},{"pid":"2c8c2d065d58a935fc5016cc0d04eaa1d5a54fc5","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T00:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg&h=e258ceb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人會買跑碟/跑輪（35cm) 比佢地玩<br />\n有無咩玩具岩佢地玩</blockquote><br />\n跑輪我覺得唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地唔似倉鼠咁細粒可以周圍走<br />\n多d放佢地出黎玩俾佢地跑跑跳跳仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb5a425871b24d37f4b0f042337ef41aea19b75","tid":25283,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T00:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知幾隻一齊養會唔會打交？</blockquote><br />\n多數唔會，佢地群居動物黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個籠一定要夠大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢兩隻係親兄弟 <br />\n有時會爭下糧 鬧兩句交咁<br />\n但嘈完兩句啊哥又會痴返細佬<br />\n雖然細佬會唔想彩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想養2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿媽唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6353b3dbc4df5a477f0c09ff48bcc2d43ceb784","tid":25283,"uid":13462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T00:21:39.000Z","msg":"養左兩隻，真係算易養，有得食就得，七年來未病過<br />\n<br />\n一隻好痴人，任抱唔嬲，另一隻就會咬人<br />\n<br />\n但係好唔好彩近年兩隻d牙都有事，睇獸醫睇到窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c285f993c642be07902cb35607e2afba667f61","tid":25283,"uid":13462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg&h=e258ceb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人會買跑碟/跑輪（35cm) 比佢地玩<br />\n有無咩玩具岩佢地玩</blockquote><br />\n我買左，佢地都幾鍾意玩<br />\n不過因為鐵做，跑起上黎有d嘈"},{"pid":"0aaa8250aff3e527c1383534120078790b9f6758","tid":25283,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"屋企果隻仔養左十七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間買過隻俾佢做伴但係打交打到損曬<br />\n之後分開養另一隻死左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家依隻好彩冇太大既病<br />\n但係都做定心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 我果隻龍貓超鐘意食蘋果<br />\n成日買王林切少少佢食<br />\n食親都勁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01be6f5d7a84ee2908938eac6d7122fbc0648867","tid":25283,"uid":18370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg&h=e258ceb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人會買跑碟/跑輪（35cm) 比佢地玩<br />\n有無咩玩具岩佢地玩</blockquote><br />\n我買左，佢地都幾鍾意玩<br />\n不過因為鐵做，跑起上黎有d嘈</blockquote><br />\n響邊買嫁？m__zoo啲跑輪太細 跑碟又成千蚊<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F174307_8b67e793a2d0455c0618c55061117c26.jpg&h=e258ceb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人會買跑碟/跑輪（35cm) 比佢地玩<br />\n有無咩玩具岩佢地玩</blockquote><br />\n跑輪我覺得唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地唔似倉鼠咁細粒可以周圍走<br />\n多d放佢地出黎玩俾佢地跑跑跳跳仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有隻放出黎都係唔郁 成日發呆 好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85265f70ebd1049813848ef335195786a12e2dbe","tid":25283,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"邊到可以買到？"}]}